# Agent guidance files.
# AGENTS.md is the single source of truth.
# CLAUDE.md and GEMINI.md at the repo root are symlinks to AGENTS.md
# (for compatibility with Claude Code, Gemini, and other agents that look for
# their specific filenames).
# The negation lines allow the root symlinks to remain tracked.
# Any additional copies in subdirectories or other locations are ignored.
CLAUDE.md
!/CLAUDE.md
GEMINI.md
!/GEMINI.md

# Secrets — sourced by .zshrc, never committed.
zsh/.zsh_secrets

# Rust build artifacts
claude/statusline/target/

# Generated tool state / caches (not project configs)
.expert/
.rumdl_cache/
